  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: When user logs in and presses device back button she is being redirected to sign in screen. Instead, the app should go into the background. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nWhen device back button is pressed, instead of going to sign in screen the app should go into background.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nWhen back button is pressed in home screen, user is redirected to sign screen. When she tries to log in again, the app crashes. \r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Sign in and wait for the home screen to appear\r\n- Press device back button\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly, April 17\r\n* Operating System: Android",
